== Citation Style
Put your own entries here in reverse chronological order. A compact format works
well for jemdoc:

~~~
. *Your Name*, Coauthor. "Paper Title." /Venue/, Year.
  ([/paper.pdf pdf], [/https://github.com/user/repo code])
~~~
